# Graffiti: Territorial Claim

**Location / Context:** Main transit corridors in the lower levels of Ceres Station, highly visible to new arrivals.
**Visual Description:** Bold, block letters, meant to be read from a distance.

**English Text:**
> __Ceres COP rock#CL9 belter.#POSS#CL2 earther#CL2 CONJ duster#CL2 go#IMP LOC home.#CL9__
"Ceres is Belter rock. Earthers and Dusters go home."
